              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>- </run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>High academic pressure</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'> paired with </run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>long study hours</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'> significantly </run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>increases depression risk</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>-Students</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'> between the </run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>ages of 16-20 years old</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'> show the </run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>highest levels of Depression</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'> despites being </run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>~13% of the population</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>-More than 60% of students</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'> have experience </run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>suicidal thoughts</run>
